{"tid":2006030,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony呢舊野其實係唔係無市場?","createTime":"2020-05-07T13:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T23:28:44.000Z","uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5d3c031e95f185e8edae527c4615a0e7750a3ad1","tid":2006030,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:24:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sony.com.hk/zh/electronics/televisions-speakers-speaker-grilles/srs-lsr100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sony.com.hk%2Fzh%2Felectronics%2Ftelevisions-speakers-speaker-grilles%2Fsrs-lsr100&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0N5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=656c77ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sony.com.hk/zh/electronics/televisions-speakers-speaker-grilles/srs-lsr100</a><br />\n<br />\n9 月 28, 2019<br />\n有位老友同巴頓講，佢老豆耳朵聽覺不太好，但夜晚睇電視就開到電視機鬼咁大聲，仲試過俾鄰居投訴，巴頓就建議呢位朋友買個 Sony SRS-LSR100 電視專用無線喇叭俾佢老豆，呢款無線喇叭使用 2.4GHz 無線傳輸，穩定性高之餘亦防干擾，配合 Voice Zoom 技術令對話更清晰，只要將無線喇叭放近身邊就可以用合適的音量聽清楚電視的聲音，仲有遙控器功能同耳機輸出，唔怕太大聲騷擾家人或鄰居，兼且適合大部分電視機使用。 SRS-LSR100 原價賣緊 $1,590 ，豐澤做緊減價 $1,340 ，平咗 $250 ，有買趁手呀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkjMpXx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkjMpXx.png&h=19903fc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6906c3d9e33301d828f27fa5a305be32476d7205","tid":2006030,"uid":151324,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:29:50.000Z","msg":"睇完成篇野都唔識點用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac3bb84a656431533c18f6312f73e30e9c76492","tid":2006030,"uid":224106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:29:55.000Z","msg":"無宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bcf8eeaa058a9613bbea2b2d17c2b7a5b7cbcc","tid":2006030,"uid":284855,"like":0,